n trading.Another thing that might happen is =E2=80=A6=C2=A0you make a ton =
of money? Schematically, imagine that VIX futures closed the previous day a=
t 30, open the day at 30, and by 4 p.m. they are trading at 45.[6] Imagine =
also that there are $2 billion of XIV notes outstanding, and Credit Suisse =
